Package com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport

Contains classes for communicating provenance information with i2 Analyze services.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardProvenance
    The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in i2 Analyze contains.
    OriginIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies the data that the CardProvenance with this OriginIdentifier describes, in its original data source.
    RetrievalBlock
    An collection of RetrievalDatums that together contain all the information necessary for i2 Analyze to retrieve the data for a Card from a particular external source.
    RetrievalBlockGlobalIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock across multiple CardProvenances.
    RetrievalBlockIdentifier
    A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock within its containing CardProvenance.
    RetrievalDatum
    A key-value pair that contains some or all of the information that i2 Analyze uses to retrieve data from an external source.
